CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, October 3, 1959, pg. A14 reads: "Out-Of-Towners - Among the guests enjoying the bicentennial dance was this group from Washington, Pa. Seated, left to right; Mrs. Leonard Mack, Mrs. Watson Mosebay Sr. Standing: Watson Mosebay Sr., William Lacey, Mrs. William Lacey, Leonard Mack, Mrs. Homer Washington, Homer Washington and Aubrey Higginbotham - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait, seated, from left: Mrs. Leonard Mack and Mrs. Watson Mosebay Sr.; Standing: Watson Mosebay Sr., William Lacey, Mrs. William Lacey, Leonard Mack, Mrs. Homer Washington, Homer Washington, and Aubrey Higginbotham, gathered in Roosevelt Hotel for the Pittsburghers Club Bicentennial dance
